      "created": "2019-04-04T18:33:40.251+0000",
      "description": "During Failover, the RM Standby\u00a0will have a lag as it has to recover from Zookeeper / FileSystem StateStore. RM HA using Ratis (Raft Protocol) can achieve Fast failover as all RMs are in sync already. This is used by Ozone - HDDS-505.\r\n\u00a0\r\ncc [~nandakumar131]",
      "priority": {
        "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/priority/3",
